scala> class A { val x: Int = 1 }
defined class A

scala> classOf[A].getDeclaredFields()(0)
res1: java.lang.reflect.Field = private final int $line7.$read$$iw$$iw$A.x
{code}
I wonder if Ammonite resolves the documentation bug already.
